data.description: Luxury awaits in this gated-side haven at The Ledges of St. George. A rare 6-car garage, expansive 0.48-acre lot, and a guest suite with a private entry and full kitchen redefine comfort. Nestled within the gated community on the Ledges golf course, this home embodies elegance and exclusivity. Indulge in a lifestyle of luxury with the exceptional amenities and meticulous craftsmanship that define this exquisite home. From its grand design to the thoughtful details, this property epitomizes sophistication and prestige. Buyer/ Buyer's agent to verify all information. The listing broker's offer of compensation is made only to participants of the MLS where the listing is filed.
